    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>,<strong> balsamic vinegar</strong>,<strong> dried basil</strong>, <strong>beef stock mix</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and 600ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[900ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.2L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Stir until combined, then bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, add your<strong> giant couscous</strong> and cook for 5 min or until beginning to soften – this is your <strong>tomato & basil broth</strong></p>",
