      "instruction": "<p>Remove the pan from the heat and stir the <strong>chopped basil</strong> through</p><p>Serve the <strong>tomato & basil broth</strong> in a bowl topped with the <strong>pork & beef polpette</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>basil leaves</strong> and sprinkle with the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
